{"tid":805300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[父母恐零回報] 子女讀IT 怕他們找不到工作","createTime":"2018-09-03T16:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T04:13:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4a0f5ea7deaaac7e9a5ab602387c4496fdbd0b04","tid":805300,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T16:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Education_Razar_01-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2FEducation_Razar_01-1.png&h=89c719ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擁有10年教電腦科經驗，負責統籌聖士提反中學STEM相關工作的伍Sir讀電腦出身。他留意到現今不少父母都有一種想法，即使子女想投身資訊科技相關的行業，亦覺得用不著今天就要選修資訊科技科目，反之會鼓吹孩子選擇傳統精英科目如M1 （微積分與統計）和 M2（代數與微積分），最理想就是入大學讀醫科或精算等被視為高人一等的科目。無奈有<span style=\"color: red;\">不少學生最後真的放棄讀電腦，埋頭書本努力去圓滿雙親期望。</span><br />\n<br />\n2000年的科網泡沫爆破令很多科網公司在霎時間破產倒閉，一下子造成數以百萬計人失業。經歷過這黑暗時代的父母，難免對IT行業有所保留，尤其當子女感興趣的是IT相關的範籌，就自然擔心子女找不到工作。說到這，伍Sir話語間流露出諒解卻又覺可惜無奈的矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/09/03/hongkong-education-academy-dream/news/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2Fhongkong-education-academy-dream%2Fnews%2F&d=zETJX9bF%2FVm68aeG15Ya3UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b03cf0ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/09/03/hongkong-education-academy-dream/news/</a>"},{"pid":"a0f54c46d1a4cc8d01aab33855454213a778ca93","tid":805300,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b300b700e20abaa39b04507ad31d9c08dc839126","tid":805300,"uid":182286,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T16:33:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fedd6ade92520f921f8c05728f6c166063f85052","tid":805300,"uid":24660,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0f54c46d1a4cc8d01aab33855454213a778ca93","tid":805300,"uid":19